    <div class="we-do">
        <p>
            We serve as a bridge of hope by connecting tribal and slum communities with dedicated NGOs and generous donors. Residents call our toll-free number, initiating a recording that captures all their needs, and the recorded request is then submitted to our website for verification before being listed for NGOs and donors. Once a request is accepted, the assisting party uploads proof of their support, triggering SMS notifications to the community. In addition, our transparent donation section displays donor names, dates, amounts, and the specific causes they support, building trust and accountability. We also facilitate coordination among NGOs to overcome logistical challenges, ensuring that every child receives the help they need.
        </p>
    </div>
